 Spinner;c;sp;ed
 '#'‚ąÜWI Pass MT‚äĘ'Reset' ‚ćĚ Clean out any previous GUI work

 :Section ‚ćĚ Check all typical on-screen buddy sizing and positioning combinations

     :Section ‚ćĚ A vertical Spinner with an Edit buddy
         'f'‚ąÜWI Pass(,'f')‚äĘ'Create' 'Form'('size' 30 100)
         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass'f.s'‚äĘ'Create' 'Spinner' ‚ćĚ Work with vertical Spinner
         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass 1.5 2.125‚äĘ'size'
         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass 14.25 48.875 1.5 2.125‚äĘ'where'

         'f.b'‚ąÜWI Pass'f.b'‚äĘ'Create' 'Edit' ‚ćĚ Let's try an Edit buddy with a default right-alignment
         'f.b'‚ąÜWI Pass 1.25 9.5‚äĘ'size'
         'f.b'‚ąÜWI Pass 14.25 45 1.5 10‚äĘ'where'
         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass MT‚äĘ'buddy' 'f.b'
         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass 1.5 2.25‚äĘ'size'
         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass 14.25 52.75 1.5 2.25‚äĘ'where'
         'f.b'‚ąÜWI Pass 1.25 7.5‚äĘ'size'
         'f.b'‚ąÜWI Pass 14.25 45 1.5 8‚äĘ'where'

         'f'‚ąÜWI Pass(,'f')‚äĘ'Create' 'Form'('size' 30 100)
         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass'f.s'‚äĘ'Create' 'Spinner'('style' 4) ‚ćĚ Work with vertical Spinner, left-aligned
         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass 1.5 2.125‚äĘ'size'
         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass 14.25 48.875 1.5 2.125‚äĘ'where'

         'f.b'‚ąÜWI Pass'f.b'‚äĘ'Create' 'Edit' ‚ćĚ Let's try Edit again but on the left side
         'f.b'‚ąÜWI Pass 1.25 9.5‚äĘ'size'
         'f.b'‚ąÜWI Pass 14.25 45 1.5 10‚äĘ'where'
         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass MT‚äĘ'buddy' 'f.b'
         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass 1.5 2.25‚äĘ'size'
         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass 14.25 45 1.5 2.25‚äĘ'where'
         'f.b'‚ąÜWI Pass 1.25 7.5‚äĘ'size'
         'f.b'‚ąÜWI Pass 14.25 47 1.5 8‚äĘ'where'

         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass MT‚äĘ'style' 8 ‚ćĚ Turn off the buddy attachment point that was previously on (so we see that it restores properly)
         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass 1.5 2.125‚äĘ'size'
         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass 14.25 48.875 1.5 2.125‚äĘ'where'
         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass'f.b'‚äĘ'buddy' ‚ćĚ Even though the buddy is still attached, it's not visibly adjacent on-screen
         'f.b'‚ąÜWI Pass 1.25 9.5‚äĘ'size'
         'f.b'‚ąÜWI Pass 14.25 45 1.5 10‚äĘ'where'

         :Section ‚ćĚ Now let's try some of that again (right-justified only) using a taller Edit control, just to make sure it keeps aligning
             'f'‚ąÜWI Pass(,'f')‚äĘ'Create' 'Form'('size' 30 100)
             'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass'f.s'‚äĘ'Create' 'Spinner' ‚ćĚ Work with vertical Spinner

             'f.b'‚ąÜWI Pass'f.b'‚äĘ'Create' 'Edit'('size' 1.75 9.5) ‚ćĚ Let's try a two-line Edit buddy
             'f.b'‚ąÜWI Pass 1.75 9.5‚äĘ'size'
             'f.b'‚ąÜWI Pass 14.125 45.25 2 10‚äĘ'where'
             'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass MT‚äĘ'buddy' 'f.b'
             'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass 2 2.25‚äĘ'size'
             'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass 14.125 53 2 2.25‚äĘ'where'
             'f.b'‚ąÜWI Pass 1.75 7.5‚äĘ'size'
             'f.b'‚ąÜWI Pass 14.125 45.25 2 8‚äĘ'where'
         :EndSection
     :EndSection

