 :EndSection

 :Section ‚ćĚ Test buddy-updating processes
     :For c :In 'Edit' 'RichEdit'('Combo'('list'(‚ćē¬®1 12 77 99))) ‚ćĚ Try the list of text-buddies
         'f'‚ąÜWI Pass(,'f')‚äĘ'Create' 'Form'('size' 30 100)
         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass'f.s'‚äĘ'Create' 'Spinner'('style' 16) ‚ćĚ Work with vertical Spinner
         'f.b'‚ąÜWI Pass'f.b'‚äĘ'Create',‚ć•‚äÜc
         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass MT‚äĘ'buddy' 'f.b'
         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass MT‚äĘ'value' 77
         'f.b'‚ąÜWI Pass'77'‚äĘ'text'
         'f.b'‚ąÜWI Pass MT‚äĘ'text' '12'
         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass 12‚äĘ'value'
     :EndFor
     :For c :In ‚äā'List'('list'(‚ćē¬®1 12 77 99)) ‚ćĚ Try the (singular list) of value-buddies
         'f'‚ąÜWI Pass(,'f')‚äĘ'Create' 'Form'('size' 30 100)
         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass'f.s'‚äĘ'Create' 'Spinner'('style' 16) ‚ćĚ Work with vertical Spinner
         'f.b'‚ąÜWI Pass'f.b'‚äĘ'Create',‚ć•‚äÜc
         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass MT‚äĘ'buddy' 'f.b'
         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass MT‚äĘ'value' 3
         'f.b'‚ąÜWI Pass(,3)‚äĘ'value'
         'f.b'‚ąÜWI Pass MT‚äĘ'value' 2
         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass 2‚äĘ'value'
     :EndFor
     :For c :In 'Label' 'Button' 'Check' 'Option' 'Frame' ‚ćĚ Try the list of caption-buddies
         'f'‚ąÜWI Pass(,'f')‚äĘ'Create' 'Form'('size' 30 100)
         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass'f.s'‚äĘ'Create' 'Spinner'('style' 16) ‚ćĚ Work with vertical Spinner
         'f.b'‚ąÜWI Pass'f.b'‚äĘ'Create',‚ć•‚äÜc
         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass MT‚äĘ'buddy' 'f.b'
         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass MT‚äĘ'value' 77
         'f.b'‚ąÜWI Pass'77'‚äĘ'caption'
         'f.b'‚ąÜWI Pass MT‚äĘ'caption' '12'
         'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass 12‚äĘ'value'
     :EndFor
 :EndSection

