 :Section ‚ćĚ Check for events firing
     'f'‚ąÜWI Pass(,'f')‚äĘ'Create' 'Form'('size' 30 100)
     'f.s'‚ąÜWI Pass'f.s'‚äĘ'Create' 'Spinner'('style' 16) ‚ćĚ Work with vertical Spinner
